                                celebrated Children's Day with a joyful and
                                engaging program organized by our dedicated
                                teachers. The day included vibrant musical
                                performances, energetic dance routines, and an
                                enchanting magic show put up by the teachers
                                that captivated the students. Dressed in
                                colorful attire, the students added to the
                                festive atmosphere. To make the occasion even
